{"expand":"renderedFields,names,schema,transitions,operations,editmeta,changelog","id":"89126","self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/latest/issue/89126","key":"PLXCOMP-133","fields":{"progress":{"progress":0,"total":0},"summary":"mvn deploy inserts target directory during jar build when using a resources section / <forced>false</forced> is not implemented","timetracking":{},"issuetype":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issuetype/1","id":"1","description":"A problem which impairs or prevents the functions of the product.","iconUrl":"http://jira.codehaus.org/images/icons/issuetypes/bug.png","name":"Bug","subtask":false},"customfield_10110":null,"votes":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/PLXCOMP-133/votes","votes":0,"hasVoted":false},"resolution":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/resolution/6","id":"6","description":"The issue is not a bug","name":"Not A Bug"},"fixVersions":[],"resolutiondate":"2009-07-03T10:40:38.130-0500","customfield_10210":"1.0","timespent":null,"reporter":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=rollantz","name":"rollantz","emailAddress":"rollantz@gmail.com","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Ronald van de Kuil","active":true},"aggregatetimeoriginalestimate":null,"customfield_10161":["bentmann(bentmann)","rollantz(rollantz)"],"customfield_10160":null,"updated":"2009-07-03T11:56:23.452-0500","created":"2009-07-03T06:26:02.037-0500","description":"I managed to trace a bug to the plexus jar archiver. \n\nSee http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MDEPLOY-105\n\nWhen I run mvn install then my jar is filled with the resources I need without the content of the target directory.\n\nWhen I run mvn deploy then my jar is updated. It then contains a directory called target/classes and in it there are the resources. \n\nThere resources are present both in the root of the jar as well as in target/classes.\n\nThe websphere service deploy task trips over this as it tries to compile the resources in target/classes\n\nI would help enormously when the <forced>false</forced> configuration of the archive is implemented as mvn install creates a JAR without the target directory.\n\nThe mvn deploy step would then leave the JAR intact.\n","priority":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/priority/3","iconUrl":"http://jira.codehaus.org/images/icons/priorities/major.png","name":"Major","id":"3"},"duedate":null,"issuelinks":[{"id":"23560","self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issueLink/23560","type":{"id":"10001","name":"dependent","inward":"is depended upon by","outward":"depends upon","self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issueLinkType/10001"},"inwardIssue":{"id":"89110","key":"MJAR-120","self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/89110","fields":{"summary":"mvn deploy inserts target directory during jar build when using a resources section","status":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/status/6","description":"The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.","iconUrl":"http://jira.codehaus.org/images/icons/statuses/closed.png","name":"Closed","id":"6"},"priority":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/priority/3","iconUrl":"http://jira.codehaus.org/images/icons/priorities/major.png","name":"Major","id":"3"},"issuetype":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issuetype/1","id":"1","description":"A problem which impairs or prevents the functions of the product.","iconUrl":"http://jira.codehaus.org/images/icons/issuetypes/bug.png","name":"Bug","subtask":false}}}}],"customfield_10163":"174614400","watches":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/PLXCOMP-133/watchers","watchCount":0